HEADWORD: Fixure
<hw>Fix"ure</hw> <pr>(-⟦usl⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fixura</ets> a fastening, fr. <ets>figere</ets> to fix. See
<er>Fix</er>, and cf. <er>Fixture</er>.]</ety> <def>Fixed position;
stable condition; firmness.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
